				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Supposing your lazy azz decides to pwrlvl a melee which is a bad idea all togethor here is a nifty trick to get those skill ups while asleep. In Ak'anon near the zonein there is a exterminator. He is LB up to lvl 46  and has like millions of HP but he only hits for 4hp dmg max. anyone lvl 10 - 46 and pull him to corner near zone in using taunt ( dont hit im until your away from other mobbs, taunt will pull him without aggroing other mobbs.) anyways pull to corner and then go afk while beating away at him left my ranger beating on him with 2hs overnight came back to a weapon skill of 200.  <img src="images/smiles/icon_biggrin.gif" alt="icon_biggrin.gif" border="0" /> hehe its great i have all my weapon skillz maxed now thanks to that wonderful weak azz exterminator.<br />_________________<br />"Are you Ron "Tater Salad" White?" "DOH you got me, you caught the Tater."</span><span class="gentblsmall"></span></td>
